<h2>Account Recovery</h2>

<p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

<p>Password reminder request has been submitted for your account at <strong>{{appName}}</strong>.</p>

<p>To set a new password and regain access, click the link below:</p>

<p class='link-text'>{{forgotUrl}}</p>

<div class='warning-box'>
  <p><strong>Important security information:</strong></p>
  <p>• For your security, this link will expire in <strong>{{expiresInMin}} minutes</strong>.</p>
</div>

<div class='divider'></div>

<p style='color: #999999; font-size: 14px;'>
  If you didn't try to recover your password, please ignore this email – your current password will remain unchanged. If you have any concerns, contact us through our website:
  <a href='{{appUrl}}/contact' style='color: #667eea;'>{{appName}}</a>.
</p>